'''穀神星地質'''是針對[[矮行星|矮行星]][[穀神星|穀神星]]的表面、外殼與內部構造的研究。

==表面與外殼組成==
穀神星的光譜遙測資料顯示它與[[C-型小行星|C-型小行星]]類似<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://irtfweb.ifa.hawaii.edu/~elv/icarus185.563.pdf |title=The surface composition of Ceres: Discovery of carbonates and iron-rich clays  |accessdate=2016-08-31 |archive-date=2007-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071128201130/http://irtfweb.ifa.hawaii.edu/~elv/icarus185.563.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，但它的光譜卻有其他C型小行星不會出現的[[碳酸鹽|碳酸鹽]]與[[黏土|黏土]]特徵，因此有時候會被列為[[G-型小行星|G-型小行星]]。穀神星的表面與[[土星的衛星|土星的衛星]][[土卫五|土卫五]]、[[土卫三|土卫三]]、[[天王星的衛星|天王星的衛星]][[天卫二|天卫二]]、[[天卫四|天卫四]]相似。

穀神星表面[[反照率|反照率]]0.09，因此和土星等外行星的衛星相較之下，穀神星表面亮度甚低。這可能是因為穀神星表面溫度相較之下較高，太陽直射時的最高溫度大約是1991年5月5日量測的235 K（約−38 °C）<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Saint-Pe|first=O.|last2=Combes|first2=M.|last3=Rigaut|first3=F.|date=1993-10-01|title=Ceres surface properties by high-resolution imaging from earth|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1993Icar..105..271S|journal=Icarus|volume=105|pages=271|doi=10.1006/icar.1993.1125|issn=0019-1035|access-date=2016-08-31|archive-date=2017-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170516170559/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1993Icar..105..271S|dead-url=no}}</ref>。真空狀態下，水冰無法在此溫度穩定存在。穀神星表面水冰昇華後留下的物質也許能解釋其表面相較於外行星衛星亮度甚低。

== 內部構造 ==
[[File:Ceres_Cutaway-en.svg|right]]
穀神星的[[扁率|扁率]]是固定的值，並且內部構造是分異的。它的核心推測是由岩石組成，並且被水冰組成的[[地函|地函]]覆蓋<ref name="Thomas2005">{{cite journal |first1=P. C. |last1=Thomas |author2=Parker, J. Wm.; McFadden, L. A. |title=Differentiation of the asteroid Ceres as revealed by its shape |year=2005 |journal=Nature |volume=437 |pages=224–226 |doi=10.1038/nature03938 |bibcode=2005Natur.437..224T |pmid=16148926 |issue=7056 |display-authors=etal}}</ref>。地函厚度約100公里，質量佔穀神星的23%-28%，體積則佔約50% <ref>72%–77%質量是無水岩石，參見William B. McKinnon (2008) [http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2008DPS....40.3803M "On The Possibility Of Large KBOs Being Injected Into The Outer Asteroid Belt"]. ''American Astronomical Society,'' DPS meeting No. 40, #38.03 {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/62D6Hmyrx?url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2008DPS....40.3803M |date=20111005152025 |dateformat=iso }}</ref>，相當於最多2億立方公里液態水，多於地球上淡水量 <ref name="Carey2006">{{cite news |url=http://space.com/scienceastronomy/050907_ceres_planet.html |title=Largest Asteroid Might Contain More Fresh Water than Earth |first=Bjorn |last=Carey |publisher=SPACE.com |date=7 September 2005 |accessdate=16 August 2006 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/62D6ITs0O?url=http://space.com/scienceastronomy/050907_ceres_planet.html |archivedate=2011年10月5日 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。這一結果得到2002年[[凱克望遠鏡|凱克望遠鏡]]的觀測與行星演化模型支持<ref name = "McCord2005-jgrp">{{cite journal |title=Ceres: Evolution and current state |journal=Journal of Geophysical Research: Planets |date=21 May 2005 |last=McCord |first=T. B. |last2=Sotin |first2=C. |volume=110 |issue=E5 |page=E05009 |doi=10.1029/2004JE002244 |url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1029/2004JE002244/full |accessdate=7 March 2015 |bibcode=2005JGRE..110.5009M |archive-date=2018-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208065851/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1029/2004JE002244/full |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Carry2008">{{cite journal |first1=Benoit |last1=Carry |title=Near-Infrared Mapping and Physical Properties of the Dwarf-Planet Ceres |year=2007 |journal=Astronomy & Astrophysics |volume=478 |issue=1 |pages=235–244 |url=http://www2.keck.hawaii.edu/inst/people/conrad/nsfGrantRef/2007-arXiv-Benoit.Carry.pdf |format=PDF |doi=10.1051/0004-6361:20078166 |bibcode=2008A&A...478..235C |arxiv=0711.1152 |display-authors=etal |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080530130946/http://www2.keck.hawaii.edu/inst/people/conrad/nsfGrantRef/2007-arXiv-Benoit.Carry.pdf |archivedate=2008年5月30日 }}</ref>。此外，穀神星表面地形特徵與地質史（例如穀神星與太陽距離讓太陽的輻射強度不足以蒸發低熔點物質，得以在穀神星形成過程中保留下來）也顯示有[[揮發成份|揮發成份]]存在於穀神星內部<ref name="Carry2008" />。有說法認為在穀神星內部的水冰層以下存在殘餘液態水（或泥濘海洋）層<ref name = "McCord2005-jgrp" /><ref name = "O'Brien2015">{{cite conference | last1 = O'Brien | first1 = D. P. | last2 = Travis | first2 = B. J. | last3 = Feldman | first3 = W. C. | last4 = Sykes | first4 = M. V. | last5 = Schenk | first5 = P. M. | last6 = Marchi | first6 = S. | last7 = Russell | first7 = C. T. | last8 = Raymond | first8 = C. A. | title = The Potential for Volcanism on Ceres due to Crustal Thickening and Pressurization of a Subsurface Ocean | booktitle = 46th [[月球與行星科學研討會|Lunar and Planetary Science Conference]] | pages = 2831 | date = March 2015 | url = http://www.hou.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2015/pdf/2831.pdf | accessdate = 1 March 2015 | archive-date = 2016-11-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161105072942/http://www.hou.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2015/pdf/2831.pdf | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。曙光號對穀神星的量測確認穀神星內部有分層結構，並且其外表是流體靜力平衡下的狀態<ref name=Lakdawalla1112>{{cite web|url=http://www.planetary.org/blogs/emily-lakdawalla/2015/dps15-1112-ceres.html|title=DPS 2015: First reconnaissance of Ceres by Dawn|publisher=|accessdate=2016-08-31|archive-date=2016-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822050249/http://www.planetary.org/blogs/emily-lakdawalla/2015/dps15-1112-ceres.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因此穀神星是太陽系內已確認流體靜力平衡天體中最小的。而土星衛星[[土卫五|土卫五]]的半徑稍低於600公里，則是已知第二小的此類天體<ref name = "Thomas2010-icarus">{{cite journal |title=Sizes, shapes, and derived properties of the saturnian satellites after the Cassini nominal mission |journal=Icarus |date=4 February 2010 |last=Thomas |first=P. C. |volume=208 |issue=1 |page=395-401 |doi=10.1016/j.icarus.2010.01.025 |url=http://www.ciclops.org/media/sp/2011/6794_16344_0.pdf |accessdate=26 August 2016 |bibcode=2010Icar..208..395T |archive-date=2011-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927185355/http://www.ciclops.org/media/sp/2011/6794_16344_0.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
